CHANGELOG

0.3.1

- Removed `pgmt` dictionary at `lib.typ` causing major processing issues.
- Fix issue with `find-pigment()` reading formatting data when searching by HEX values.
- Fix contrast color with search results background.
- Improve error handling.
- Update documentation.
- Other minor improvements.

0.3.0

- Fix issue with scoped search.
- Add Pigmentpedia logo.
- Add sample document for testing pigments.
- Visual layout improvements.
- Update pigment groups.
- Update documentation.
- Other bug fixes, code improvements and optimization.

0.2.0

- Add more pigments and 8 color standards.
- Create functions for searching and displaying pigments.

0.1.0

- Initial release with a 149 colors.
